<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Update Address Confirm</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .email_container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .header {
            position: relative;
            border-radius: 12px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            background-color: {{ shopColor }};
            color: #ffffff;
            text-align: center;
        }

        h4 {
            font-size: 24px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 52px 59px;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", "Roboto", "Oxygen", "Ubuntu", "Cantarell", "Fira Sans", "Droid Sans", "Helvetica Neue", sans-serif;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .b_id {
            color: {{ shopColor }};
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .highlight {
            color: {{ shopColor }};
        }

        .footer {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", "Roboto", "Oxygen", "Ubuntu", "Cantarell", "Fira Sans", "Droid Sans", "Helvetica Neue", sans-serif;
            font-weight: 500;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #888888;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="email_container">
        <div class="header">
            <img width="100%" src="cid:top_banner">
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <h5 class="subject">Subject: Your Shipping Address Has Been Updated</h5>
            <h4>Dear {{ customerName }},</h4>
            <p>
                We hope you're doing well! We're reaching out to confirm that the shipping address for your order
                <b class="b_id">({{ orderName }})</b> has been successfully updated. Please review the new address below to
                ensure it is correct.
                <br><br>
                <span class="highlight">New Shipping Address:</span><br>
                {{ newAddress }}
                <br><br>
                If this address is correct, no further action is needed, and your order will be shipped as scheduled.
                However, if there is an issue, please <a href="{{ contactPage }}">contact us</a> as soon as possible so we can assist you.
                <br><br>
                At <span class="highlight">{{ shopName }},</span> we value your trust and are committed to providing the
                best experience for women who prioritize self-care and well-being. If you have any questions or need
                further assistance, feel free to reach out.
                <br><br>
                Thank you for choosing us!
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2025 {{ shopName }}. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>